  "beats": [
    {
      "zh": "你有没有发现，有的家庭明明不缺钱，日子却越过越乱？",
      "scene": "S2-01",
      "en": "Some homes aren't broke, yet life keeps fraying.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-01.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 4640
    },
    {
      "zh": "有的家条件一般，反而越过越顺？",
      "scene": "S2-01",
      "en": "while plainer ones somehow keep getting smoother?",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-01.mp3",
      "audioStart": 4640,
      "audioEnd": 7760
    },
    {
      "zh": "差别往往不是钱，而是这五个字：家和万事兴。",
      "scene": "S2-01",
      "en": "The gap isn't money — it's home harmony.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-01.mp3",
      "audioStart": 7760,
      "audioEnd": 12513
    },
    {
      "zh": "很多人把这话当鸡汤，",
      "scene": "S2-02",
      "en": "People call that a cliché,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-02.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 1760
    },
    {
      "zh": "可人到中年，上有老下有小你就懂了，",
      "scene": "S2-02",
      "en": "but in midlife, you finally understand —",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-02.mp3",
      "audioStart": 1760,
      "audioEnd": 6240
    },
    {
      "zh": "一个家最大的本事，就是夫妻还能好好说话。",
      "scene": "S2-02",
      "en": "a home's strength is a couple still talking kindly.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-02.mp3",
      "audioStart": 6240,
      "audioEnd": 10344
    },
    {
      "zh": "古人为什么把“和”看得这么重？",
      "scene": "S2-03",
      "en": "Why did the ancients prize harmony so?",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-03.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 3120
    },
    {
      "zh": "唐代张公艺九世同堂，皇帝问秘诀，",
      "scene": "S2-03",
      "en": "One elder kept nine generations under one roof.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-03.mp3",
      "audioStart": 3120,
      "audioEnd": 6960
    },
    {
      "zh": "他没有长篇大论，只写了一个字：忍。",
      "scene": "S2-03",
      "en": "His secret was a single word: forbear.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-03.mp3",
      "audioStart": 6960,
      "audioEnd": 11233
    },
    {
      "zh": "但这个忍，不是委曲求全，不是把气憋进身体，",
      "scene": "S2-04",
      "en": "To forbear isn't to swallow your anger,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-04.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 5360
    },
    {
      "zh": "而是火气上头时先收一收，",
      "scene": "S2-04",
      "en": "it's easing off when your temper flares,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-04.mp3",
      "audioStart": 5360,
      "audioEnd": 8080
    },
    {
      "zh": "给彼此留体面，给全家留退路。",
      "scene": "S2-04",
      "en": "leaving dignity, and a way out for all.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-04.mp3",
      "audioStart": 8080,
      "audioEnd": 12199
    },
    {
      "zh": "因为中年夫妻一旦失和，",
      "scene": "S2-05",
      "en": "Once a midlife couple falls out,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-05.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2320
    },
    {
      "zh": "上面是老人提心吊胆，",
      "scene": "S2-05",
      "en": "the elders live on edge,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-05.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2320,
      "audioEnd": 4400
    },
    {
      "zh": "下面是孩子耳濡目染，家里很快就鸡飞狗跳。",
      "scene": "S2-05",
      "en": "the kids absorb it, and home turns to chaos.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-05.mp3",
      "audioStart": 4400,
      "audioEnd": 8908
    },
    {
      "zh": "你以为只是吵一架，",
      "scene": "S2-06",
      "en": "You think it's just one quarrel,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-06.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 1920
    },
    {
      "zh": "其实老人心情糟糕，孩子没有安全感，",
      "scene": "S2-06",
      "en": "but elders feel low and kids feel unsafe,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-06.mp3",
      "audioStart": 1920,
      "audioEnd": 5520
    },
    {
      "zh": "连吃饭睡觉都变得战战兢兢，时间久了孩子都不愿回家。",
      "scene": "S2-06",
      "en": "even meals and sleep grow tense — kids avoid home.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-06.mp3",
      "audioStart": 5520,
      "audioEnd": 11468
    },
    {
      "zh": "科学上早就解释过，",
      "scene": "S2-07",
      "en": "Science explained this long ago:",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-07.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2160
    },
    {
      "zh": "家庭里的情绪会传染，一个人黑脸，全屋神经都会绷紧，",
      "scene": "S2-07",
      "en": "moods spread — one sour face tightens the house,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-07.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2160,
      "audioEnd": 7440
    },
    {
      "zh": "长期待在这种环境，孩子更容易焦虑、暴躁。",
      "scene": "S2-07",
      "en": "live in that and kids grow anxious, short-tempered.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-07.mp3",
      "audioStart": 7440,
      "audioEnd": 11807
    },
    {
      "zh": "更关键的是，孩子学的从来不是你说什么，",
      "scene": "S2-08",
      "en": "Kids don't learn from what you say,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-08.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 3920
    },
    {
      "zh": "而是你怎么对家人，怎么对老人，怎么处理冲突，",
      "scene": "S2-08",
      "en": "but from how you treat family and conflict —",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-08.mp3",
      "audioStart": 3920,
      "audioEnd": 7920
    },
    {
      "zh": "这就叫上行下效，也是最深的耳濡目染。",
      "scene": "S2-08",
      "en": "that's leading by example — the deepest lesson.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-08.mp3",
      "audioStart": 7920,
      "audioEnd": 12356
    },
    {
      "zh": "从身体反应看，夫妻天天冷战争吵，",
      "scene": "S2-09",
      "en": "When a couple bickers and stonewalls daily,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-09.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 3520
    },
    {
      "zh": "睡眠会乱，火气会大，长期紧张时皮质醇也会居高不下，",
      "scene": "S2-09",
      "en": "sleep frays, tempers rise, stress runs high,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-09.mp3",
      "audioStart": 3520,
      "audioEnd": 8800
    },
    {
      "zh": "人一累，判断就容易失准，话越来越硬，事越办越拧。",
      "scene": "S2-09",
      "en": "worn out, judgment slips and words harden.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-09.mp3",
      "audioStart": 8800,
      "audioEnd": 14106
    },
    {
      "zh": "所以很多家庭不是败给贫穷，",
      "scene": "S2-10",
      "en": "Many families aren't beaten by poverty,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-10.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2880
    },
    {
      "zh": "是败给内耗，",
      "scene": "S2-10",
      "en": "but by infighting,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-10.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2880,
      "audioEnd": 4400
    },
    {
      "zh": "一边拼命挣钱，一边互相伤人，一边把福气往门外推。",
      "scene": "S2-10",
      "en": "earning hard while pushing their luck out the door.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-10.mp3",
      "audioStart": 4400,
      "audioEnd": 9326
    },
    {
      "zh": "传统文化认为，和气聚财，戾气散福，",
      "scene": "S2-11",
      "en": "Harmony draws wealth; spite drains fortune,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-11.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 3840
    },
    {
      "zh": "一个家天天摔门拍桌，再好的风水也压不住怨气，",
      "scene": "S2-11",
      "en": "no feng shui saves a home of slammed doors,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-11.mp3",
      "audioStart": 3840,
      "audioEnd": 8480
    },
    {
      "zh": "一个家常年好声好气，粗茶淡饭也能养出福报。",
      "scene": "S2-11",
      "en": "kind words breed blessings on the plainest meals.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-11.mp3",
      "audioStart": 8480,
      "audioEnd": 13244
    },
    {
      "zh": "别觉得家和只是面子工程，",
      "scene": "S2-12",
      "en": "Harmony isn't just for show —",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-12.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2160
    },
    {
      "zh": "对老人来说，那是安心；对孩子来说，那是底气；",
      "scene": "S2-12",
      "en": "to elders it's peace, to kids it's confidence,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-12.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2160,
      "audioEnd": 6640
    },
    {
      "zh": "对夫妻自己来说，那是熬过中年的续命能量。",
      "scene": "S2-12",
      "en": "to the couple, the fuel to outlast midlife.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-12.mp3",
      "audioStart": 6640,
      "audioEnd": 10606
    },
    {
      "zh": "尤其是中年夫妻，白天在外面扛压力，",
      "scene": "S2-13",
      "en": "By day you carry the pressure outside;",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-13.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 3360
    },
    {
      "zh": "晚上回家如果还是针尖对麦芒，",
      "scene": "S2-13",
      "en": "if home at night is still a battlefield,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-13.mp3",
      "audioStart": 3360,
      "audioEnd": 5840
    },
    {
      "zh": "人会越来越累，家也会越来越冷。",
      "scene": "S2-13",
      "en": "you grow wearier, and home grows colder.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-13.mp3",
      "audioStart": 5840,
      "audioEnd": 8829
    },
    {
      "zh": "真正的家和，不是谁永远赢，",
      "scene": "S2-14",
      "en": "Real harmony isn't about who wins,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-14.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2560
    },
    {
      "zh": "而是遇事先对事不对人，先商量不翻旧账，",
      "scene": "S2-14",
      "en": "it's facing the issue, not raking up the past,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-14.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2560,
      "audioEnd": 6960
    },
    {
      "zh": "先顾全大局，再解决问题。",
      "scene": "S2-14",
      "en": "big picture first, then fix the problem.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-14.mp3",
      "audioStart": 6960,
      "audioEnd": 9796
    },
    {
      "zh": "该让的时候让一步，叫相敬如宾，",
      "scene": "S2-15",
      "en": "Yield when you should — that's respect,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-15.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 3120
    },
    {
      "zh": "该暖的时候暖一句，叫同心同德，",
      "scene": "S2-15",
      "en": "warm up when you should — that's one heart,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-15.mp3",
      "audioStart": 3120,
      "audioEnd": 6320
    },
    {
      "zh": "夫妻和睦，老人安稳，孩子向阳，这个家才会越来越旺。",
      "scene": "S2-15",
      "en": "spouses aligned, kids thriving — a home rises.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-15.mp3",
      "audioStart": 6320,
      "audioEnd": 12199
    },
    {
      "zh": "所以为什么说家和万事兴？",
      "scene": "S2-16",
      "en": "So why does a harmonious home thrive?",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-16.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2960
    },
    {
      "zh": "因为和，是一个家的秩序、运气和前程，",
      "scene": "S2-16",
      "en": "Harmony is a home's order, luck, and future,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-16.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2960,
      "audioEnd": 7200
    },
    {
      "zh": "房子再大，吵着过像牢笼；笑着吃饭才是人间烟火。",
      "scene": "S2-16",
      "en": "a quarrelsome house is a cage; smiles make a home.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-16.mp3",
      "audioStart": 7200,
      "audioEnd": 12513
    },
    {
      "zh": "家和，不一定让你立刻大富大贵，",
      "scene": "S2-17",
      "en": "Harmony won't make you rich overnight,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-17.mp3",
      "audioStart": 0,
      "audioEnd": 2800
    },
    {
      "zh": "但一定能让你少走弯路，少生闲气，少败福报，",
      "scene": "S2-17",
      "en": "but it spares you detours and wasted blessings,",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-17.mp3",
      "audioStart": 2800,
      "audioEnd": 6880
    },
    {
      "zh": "把一地鸡毛的日子，慢慢过成细水长流。<END>",
      "scene": "S2-17",
      "en": "turning a messy life into a calm, lasting stream.",
      "audioFile": "audio/scene-S2-17.mp3",
      "audioStart": 6880,
      "audioEnd": 10841
    }
  ],
